title: Drew Gilliland leads Mitchell over Chadron
text:
CON MARSHALL Drew Gilliland leads Mitchell over Chadron 
Mitchell quarterback Drew Gilliland tries to run away from Chadron defender Marquis Burwell during the second half of their game in Chadron Friday night. Posted: Friday, October 2, 2015 11:57 pm Drew Gilliland leads Mitchell over Chadron CON MARSHALL For the Star-Herald Star Herald CHADRON — Senior quarterback Drew Gilliland ran for three touchdowns and threw for a fourth here Friday night as the Mitchell Tigers rallied for a 27-15 victory over Chadron. The Tigers, now 5-1 on the season, broke a scoreless stalemate with 8:43 to play in the second quarter on Gilliland’s 79-yard run down the Mitchell sideline on what coach Jimmie Rhodes called “a counter play.”   Remember me on this computer Login Or, use your linked account: facebook Need an account?
